    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Forest 6174</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A BRIEF FIRST-PERSON PSYCHOLOGICAL HORROR EXPERIENCE</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Danny, an exceptional individual. Danny is cooperative. Danny follows the rules. No matter how bad he feels, Danny is always ready to smile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But one day, Danny is summoned. Not for a promotion. Not for a reprimand. Just to be given a break, some time out of his routine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, Danny is lost in the darkness of the forest, a place where logic crumbles and events defy reality. To find a way out, he must unravel the secret that lies deep within.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162920/extras/039c0fb4b3d47b3a0d69e2eabb5e1183.poster.avif?t=1753794821\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162920/extras/039c0fb4b3d47b3a0d69e2eabb5e1183.webm?t=1753794821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162920/extras/039c0fb4b3d47b3a0d69e2eabb5e1183.mp4?t=1753794821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forest 6174 offers an immersive first-person experience that combines psychological and atmospheric horror.  The narrative unfolds through subtle interactions with the environment. Explore an eerie location and uncover fragments of the story as you progress.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 - 25 minutes of gameplay.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric environment: Each level and the accompanying sounds are part of an immersive experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Psychological horror: The game presents situations in which you do not know if they are real or in your head.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you pay attention you will discover some interesting details.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The game has a unique ending.</strong></p>",
